  "description": "Div Acer Manager Max is a Linux GUI for Acer laptops using Linuwu Sense drivers. It replicates NitroSense functionality with fan control, performance modes, battery limiter, and more. Built with Avalonia, it offers a clean, easy-to-use interface for managing system performance and cooling.",
